text: Roman Olehovych Yaremchuk (Ukrainian: Роман Олегович Яремчук; born 27 November 1995) is a Ukrainian professional footballer who plays as a striker for Belgian First Division A club Club Brugge and the Ukraine national team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Lviv Category:UEFA Euro 2024 players
title: Roman Yaremchuk
